data.description: Discover the perfect blend of tranquility and modern living in this charming double-wide mobile home on a permanent foundation, nestled on a spacious .33-acre lot, right along the Sapelo River. Whether you're seeking a peaceful getaway or a permanent residence, this property offers a unique lifestyle opportunity. inside you will find a primary bedroom with a walk-in shower and also a garden tub. You can stay cozy in the living room with the gas fireplace or hang outside in the beautiful nature of Sapelo Gardens. Outside this home you get a 2 car carport to cover that dream-ride or your next off-shore boat. There is also 2 storage sheds that are located on this property. There is a community Dock/Dockhouse available for HOA members steps away from this slice of tranquility. HOA is voluntary, not mandatory.
